Description: Package for processing mass spectrometry-based metabolomics files. 
	     The accepted file formats are '.mzXML' and '.mzML'. The processing steps 
	     combine deconvolute functions, spectra annotation, quantification and 
	     basic statistics functions, with automatically generated images for 
	     performance evaluation and result interpretation. Additionally, the 
	     package can process standard compounds analysis files for internal library
	     development.
